<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />Why should I fear those who trust in their wealth</para>

<para style="q1">and boast about the amount of their riches?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />It is certain that no one can redeem his brother</para>

<para style="q1">or give God a ransom for him,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />For the redemption of one's life is costly,</para>

<para style="q1">and no one can pay what we owe.</para>
